metadata.name: Big whale
metadata.description:
This is a steep cliff that keeps people away, beyond that is the beautiful Milky Way.  Appearance of the cliff is like a big whale. I imagined that the whale swiming in the sea go back to the far end of the galaxy.
And a line of meteor make a impressive landscape.
